      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>零食年货商城</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        color: #4E342E;\n    }\n    header {\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: center;\n        align-items: center;\n        padding: 10px;\n        background-color: #C62828;\n    }\n    header input {\n        padding: 8px;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        margin-right: 5px;\n        flex: 1;\n    }\n    header button {\n        padding: 8px 16px;\n        background-color: #FFD54F;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    nav {\n        background-color: #FFCCBC;\n    }\n    nav ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-around;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 10px 0;\n    }\n    nav li {\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    section {\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    #product-gallery img {\n        width: 100%;\n        max-height: 300px;\n        object-fit: cover;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    #product-gallery .thumbs {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n    }\n    #product-gallery .thumbs img {\n        width: 60px;\n        height: 60px;\n        object-fit: cover;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #price-promotion p {\n        font-size: 1.2em;\n        color: #C62828;\n    }\n    #price-promotion .promotion {\n        margin-top: 10px;\n        background-color: #FFD54F;\n        padding: 10px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #price-promotion .tag {\n        display: inline-block;\n        background-color: #C62828;\n        color: #fff;\n        padding: 4px 8px;\n        margin-top: 8px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #coupon-section {\n        background-color: #FFCCBC;\n        padding: 15px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    #coupon-section .coupon-list {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #coupon-section button {\n        padding: 8px 16px;\n        background-color: #C62828;\n        color: #fff;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #specification-selector {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 8px;\n    }\n    #purchase-channel {\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: center;\n        padding: 15px;\n        background-color: #C62828;\n    }\n    #purchase-channel button {\n        padding: 12px 20px;\n        font-size: 1.2em;\n        background-color: #FFD54F;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #comments-filter ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n    #comments-filter ul li {\n        background-color: #FFCCBC;\n        padding: 6px 12px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #cart-modal {\n        position: fixed;\n        top: 50%;\n        left: 50%;\n        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n        background-color: #fff;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        width: 80%;\n        max-width: 400px;\n        display: none;\n    }\n    #cart-modal h2 {\n        margin-top: 0;\n    }\n    #cart-modal button {\n        padding: 8px 16px;\n        background-color: #C62828;\n        color: #fff;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<header id=\"search-bar\">\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"搜索零食或年货\">\n    <button>搜索</button>\n</header>\n\n<nav id=\"nav-bar\">\n    <ul>\n        <li>首页</li>\n        <li>活动</li>\n        <li>购物车</li>\n        <li>个人中心</li>\n    </ul>\n</nav>\n\n<section id=\"product-gallery\">\n    <img src=\"kuihuazi-large.jpg\" alt=\"葵花籽产品\">\n    <div class=\"thumbs\">\n        <img src=\"thumb1.jpg\" alt=\"缩略图1\">\n        <img src=\"thumb2.jpg\" alt=\"缩略图2\">\n        <img src=\"thumb3.jpg\" alt=\"缩略图3\">\n    </div>\n    <p>美味葵花籽，香脆可口，精选优质原料。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"price-promotion\">\n    <p>现价：¥19.9 <del>原价：¥29.9</del></p>\n    <div class=\"promotion\">限时促销倒计时：00:12:45</div>\n    <span class=\"tag\">热卖中</span>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"coupon-section\">\n    <div class=\"coupon-list\">\n        <p>满100减20</p>\n        <p>满50减5</p>\n    </div>\n    <button>领取优惠券</button>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"specification-selector\">\n    <label>\n        规格：\n        <select>\n            <option>10包</option>\n            <option>20包</option>\n            <option>30包</option>\n        </select>\n    </label>\n    <div>单价更优惠，买得越多省得越多！</div>\n</section>\n\n<footer id=\"purchase-channel\">\n    <button>立即购买</button>\n</footer>\n\n<section id=\"comments-filter\">\n    <ul>\n        <li>好评</li>\n        <li>差评</li>\n        <li>晒图</li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"comment-list\">\n        <p>用户A：口感不错，包装精致。</p>\n        <p>用户B：送货很快，味道好。</p>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<div id=\"cart-modal\">\n    <h2>购物车</h2>\n    <div>葵花籽 20包</div>\n    <p>优惠价：¥39.8 结算信息：包含运费</p>\n    <button>支付</button>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
